name: Cat Vs Dog － Cat fight to dog
name_original: Cat Vs Dog － Cat fight to dog
description:
The Dog occupy the home of The Cat. So,the caat has to fight with the dog.Let us help cat and let the dog go.Be carefull,make sure don't let the cat hurt.
In the game your goal is to make the dog out of screen or touch the sharp knife or touch magma.
This game the arts of cat and dog is cute.Music is nice too.
